Package: heplots
Type: Package
Title: Visualizing Tests in Multivariate Linear Models
Version: 0.9-8
Date: 2010-11-04
Author@R: c(person(given = "John", family = "Fox"),
            person(given = "Michael", family = "Friendly"),
            person(given = "Georges", family = "Monette"))
Author: John Fox, Michael Friendly, and Georges Monette
Maintainer: Michael Friendly <friendly@yorku.ca>
Depends: car, graphics, stats
Suggests: rgl, candisc, effects, reshape, gplots, nlme, lattice
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Description: Provides HE plot functions for visualizing hypothesis tests in multivariate linear models. They represents sums-of-squares-and-products matrices for linear hypotheses and for error using ellipses (in two dimensions) and ellipsoids (in three dimensions).
License: GPL version 2 or newer
